  <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H \colon  f \sim  g]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopy</fr:link> between two functions <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f,g\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. For any identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  x =y]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, we have an identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H x \cdot  \mathsf {act}_{g}\,p = \mathsf {act}_{f}\,p\cdot  Hy]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>21</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001V/0</fr:addr><fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001V/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="naturality of homotopies › forest://erct/erct-001V/0"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001V.xml" title="naturality of homotopies" addr="forest://erct/erct-001V" type="local">naturality of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopies</fr:link></fr:link> › forest://erct/erct-001V/0</fr:title><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
